                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370814-2018-offence-1 t18370814-cd-215"></join>13th of July</rs>, 1 boat, value 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 sculls, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370814-name-1417" type="victimName">
